WEBVTT

01:51.660 --> 01:57.500
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.590 --> 02:01.940
[Episode 7]

02:02.110 --> 02:02.670
Here.

02:03.190 --> 02:04.250
Careful, it's hot.

02:18.480 --> 02:19.370
What's wrong?

02:22.790 --> 02:23.480
Nothing.

02:25.040 --> 02:25.550
Here.

02:26.110 --> 02:26.670
Careful.

02:39.470 --> 02:40.320
Master,

02:40.840 --> 02:41.990
Fan Yun is awake.

02:43.170 --> 02:46.430
He really found the Myriad-Spirit Herb.

02:46.770 --> 02:48.050
They say

02:48.079 --> 02:49.740
the Dark Wolves presented it.

02:51.240 --> 02:52.860
Then it seems the people
who rescued Fan Yun

02:52.860 --> 02:54.380
from Linglong Tower

02:54.430 --> 02:56.079
really were Dark Wolves.

02:57.520 --> 02:58.690
To think

02:59.300 --> 03:01.720
he actually found the Dark Wolves.

03:06.240 --> 03:07.540
It seems Qi Zheng

03:08.210 --> 03:10.530
really isn't entirely useless,

03:11.190 --> 03:13.090
just as Gao Ran said.

03:14.320 --> 03:15.200
Master,

03:15.850 --> 03:17.750
since coming back
from the morning audience,

03:17.750 --> 03:19.940
you don't seem to be in a very good mood.

03:20.310 --> 03:21.840
The assassination failed,

03:23.040 --> 03:25.930
and Gao Ran also refused to
take on this task.

03:26.500 --> 03:28.310
And now the Governor

03:29.100 --> 03:31.570
has Dark Wolves protecting him as well.

03:33.360 --> 03:35.340
You mentioned last time that Suyin

03:35.960 --> 03:37.050
was taken away?

03:37.980 --> 03:38.640
Yes.

03:42.340 --> 03:44.720
If Suyin hadn't acted on her own

03:44.750 --> 03:45.950
to carry out the poisoning,

03:45.950 --> 03:48.210
I wouldn't be
in such a disadvantaged position.

03:48.210 --> 03:50.930
At this point,
she'll have to bear this herself.

03:52.030 --> 03:52.710
Master,

03:53.220 --> 03:54.570
you mean...

04:05.180 --> 04:06.950
Who would have thought

04:08.200 --> 04:10.920
that a momentary act of kindness back then

04:11.580 --> 04:14.720
would nearly become my weakness?

04:17.570 --> 04:18.600
It seems

04:20.230 --> 04:22.060
that to achieve great things,

04:22.930 --> 04:25.320
one cannot afford to be soft-hearted.

04:32.190 --> 04:33.390
Abandon her.

04:35.740 --> 04:36.370
Fan Yun,

04:37.570 --> 04:38.840
Suyin's life is now

04:40.450 --> 04:41.570
in your hands.

05:00.770 --> 05:01.580
Suyin,

05:02.810 --> 05:04.410
lift your head and look at me.

05:11.190 --> 05:12.570
I said, lift your head

05:12.790 --> 05:13.620
and look at me.

05:19.560 --> 05:20.960
Right now, I just hope...

05:22.760 --> 05:23.960
you can step forward

05:24.870 --> 05:26.480
and testify against Lord Zheng.

05:26.480 --> 05:27.450
Not for yourself,

05:27.450 --> 05:29.510
but for the people of the Nine Cities.

05:31.780 --> 05:32.750
Can you do that?

05:47.800 --> 05:48.530
Here.

05:49.280 --> 05:49.880
Slow down.

05:53.290 --> 05:54.100
Eat.

05:54.130 --> 05:56.130
When you're full, come home with me.

06:29.830 --> 06:30.840
Can you?

06:30.860 --> 06:31.890
Answer me.

06:31.920 --> 06:33.720
I won't give you a second chance.

06:34.640 --> 06:35.520
Suyin.

06:36.720 --> 06:38.380
If that's your firm decision,

06:39.180 --> 06:41.380
I'll deal with you according to the law.

06:42.210 --> 06:43.740
I'll count down from three.

06:45.240 --> 06:45.870
Three!

06:48.040 --> 06:48.750
Two!

06:49.190 --> 06:49.950
Suyin.

06:52.500 --> 06:53.100
One!

06:53.159 --> 06:53.940
Answer me!

07:00.470 --> 07:01.760
Suyin!

07:02.930 --> 07:03.980
Suyin!

07:13.560 --> 07:14.530
You...

07:18.310 --> 07:18.920
Suyin...

07:19.720 --> 07:20.480
Suyin!

07:21.310 --> 07:22.240
Suyin!

07:24.870 --> 07:25.720
Suyin...

07:26.370 --> 07:26.930
Hurry,

07:27.240 --> 07:28.300
fetch a physician!

07:28.480 --> 07:29.540
Fetch a physician!

07:29.730 --> 07:30.350
Fetch a physician!

07:30.350 --> 07:31.030
Fan Yun!

07:31.750 --> 07:32.840
Are you going to defy my order?

07:32.840 --> 07:34.840
But didn't you just say

07:34.870 --> 07:36.670
this was for me to decide?

07:36.690 --> 07:38.490
Since what she wanted

07:38.520 --> 07:40.580
was to serve only one master for life—

07:41.159 --> 07:42.690
I've granted her that wish.

07:43.340 --> 07:44.460
A person like her

07:45.480 --> 07:46.680
is not worth keeping.

07:51.159 --> 07:51.800
Suyin...

07:53.159 --> 07:54.120
Suyin...

07:55.720 --> 07:57.040
Hang in there.

07:58.120 --> 07:58.950
Suyin.

07:59.920 --> 08:00.680
Hurry.

08:01.160 --> 08:02.270
Physician...

08:02.420 --> 08:04.130
Fetch a physician!

08:30.960 --> 08:33.830
He really is an impulsive young fool.

08:35.730 --> 08:37.140
If Gao Ran hadn't

08:37.159 --> 08:39.320
rejected it so resolutely...

08:39.380 --> 08:40.289
Either way,

08:41.110 --> 08:42.870
dead men tell no tales.

08:44.750 --> 08:45.480
In that case,

08:46.210 --> 08:48.210
we have to consider

08:49.000 --> 08:50.120
how to move forward

08:50.140 --> 08:51.730
from here.

08:53.190 --> 08:54.860
Suyin is dead.

08:55.260 --> 08:57.020
She served you for many years.

08:57.110 --> 08:58.110
Though reckless,

08:58.620 --> 08:59.460
she was loyal

08:59.480 --> 09:00.570
to you.

09:01.320 --> 09:02.560
Qi Zheng

09:02.720 --> 09:03.750
may not necessarily know that this was...

09:03.750 --> 09:04.910
You may leave.

09:05.520 --> 09:06.250
Yes, Master.

10:04.770 --> 10:05.530
I...

10:05.560 --> 10:06.610
How did I...

10:09.100 --> 10:11.900
I'm responsible for
escorting you out of the city.

10:11.920 --> 10:12.850
You're free now.

10:19.320 --> 10:20.080
This is

10:20.540 --> 10:22.470
a letter from the Governor for you.

10:30.350 --> 10:31.730
"The situation was urgent,

10:31.730 --> 10:33.850
so I had no choice
but to resort to this plan.

10:33.850 --> 10:35.740
The carriage will take you
out of the city.

10:35.740 --> 10:37.810
You would not betray the one you trust—

10:37.810 --> 10:39.140
that is your integrity.

10:39.340 --> 10:41.340
I should've respected your choice.

10:41.640 --> 10:44.040
But seeing how deeply
my wife cares for you,

10:44.160 --> 10:46.090
I couldn't bear to break her heart.

10:46.730 --> 10:47.570
Remember:

10:48.030 --> 10:50.360
you've already died once for that person.

10:50.850 --> 10:52.210
My wife is the one

10:52.780 --> 10:54.510
who gave you this second life."

11:18.750 --> 11:19.770
What's wrong?

11:29.790 --> 11:30.520
Turns out...

11:31.840 --> 11:34.170
Turns out all of you
were putting on an act.

11:34.270 --> 11:36.470
Then why didn't you tell me beforehand?

11:36.510 --> 11:37.320
If we'd told you beforehand,

11:37.320 --> 11:39.650
the act wouldn't have been so convincing.

11:39.720 --> 11:40.360
Besides,

11:41.230 --> 11:43.100
I wouldn't have done it if I hadn't been

11:43.100 --> 11:44.640
completely confident it would work.

11:44.640 --> 11:46.240
Suyin is fine now, isn't she?

11:47.750 --> 11:48.460
Right?

11:53.810 --> 11:54.690
Come on.

11:56.020 --> 11:57.820
I should've told you in advance.

12:02.880 --> 12:04.600
I'm not mad.

12:08.870 --> 12:11.110
I just wonder—in the eyes of the nobles,

12:12.000 --> 12:14.200
are human lives really worth so little?

12:16.430 --> 12:18.190
It's fine if you're angry.

12:18.210 --> 12:19.290
I'll stay with you.

12:23.080 --> 12:26.400
♪ Watch how flowers bloom and wither ♪

12:26.990 --> 12:30.490
♪ Count how many springs
and autumns pass ♪

12:30.830 --> 12:32.830
♪ Why the sighs and regrets? ♪

12:39.240 --> 12:42.540
♪ Lovers wait a lifetime ♪

12:43.030 --> 12:46.170
♪ Love cannot be cut away ♪

12:46.740 --> 12:49.530
♪ How to let go? ♪

12:55.290 --> 12:58.640
♪ All our fates were long inscribed ♪

12:58.990 --> 13:02.650
♪ How to set free grief and joy? ♪

13:03.220 --> 13:04.940
♪ Mortal life is but an ephemeral dream ♪

13:05.350 --> 13:10.900
♪ No mortal soul may rule its life ♪

13:11.280 --> 13:12.770
♪ If women are akin to blossoms ♪

13:12.810 --> 13:15.150
♪ Can they be cherished tenderly? ♪

13:15.310 --> 13:18.480
♪ For whom do they hide tears silently? ♪

13:18.760 --> 13:20.980
♪ How could one bear to lay blame? ♪

13:21.000 --> 13:23.370
♪ Time runs wild with reckless haste ♪

13:23.400 --> 13:27.100
♪ Never mind fate dyes white crimson red ♪

13:27.410 --> 13:28.750
♪ For whom does ♪

13:28.770 --> 13:30.940
♪ This phoenix blossom bloom? ♪

13:30.970 --> 13:34.940
♪ Love fills my years,
and my heart remains true ♪

13:35.170 --> 13:37.220
♪ Let all worldly longing fade away ♪

13:37.250 --> 13:39.640
♪ Fall deep within a single dream ♪

13:39.740 --> 13:48.190
♪ Wait till a breath of wind arrives ♪

16:39.270 --> 16:40.270
Zheng Yuan!

16:45.600 --> 16:46.600
Your Excellency.

16:49.590 --> 16:51.320
Is Your Excellency going to...

16:51.320 --> 16:52.080
Zheng Yuan,

16:53.240 --> 16:54.770
I have something to ask you.

16:56.030 --> 16:56.940
I'll

16:56.960 --> 16:58.870
hold nothing back, Your Excellency.

16:58.870 --> 17:00.320
Ask yourself:

17:01.120 --> 17:01.950
have you been

17:02.400 --> 17:03.960
a good official?

17:05.950 --> 17:07.430
Have you been loyal to me

17:07.810 --> 17:09.130
and to the Nine Cities?

17:10.109 --> 17:12.510
Why would Your Excellency
ask such a thing?

17:13.670 --> 17:15.329
I would sacrifice everything

17:15.839 --> 17:17.250
for Your Excellency,

17:18.790 --> 17:20.260
for the Nine Cities—

17:22.440 --> 17:24.829
and I already have.

17:27.740 --> 17:29.610
But the Nine Cities

17:29.630 --> 17:30.960
are on the verge of ruin!

17:31.630 --> 17:32.760
Your Excellency...

17:43.590 --> 17:49.040
Zheng Yuan! Zheng Yuan!

17:49.200 --> 17:51.110
How can you live with yourself?

18:08.270 --> 18:09.000
Shi.

18:09.640 --> 18:11.050
Come, come.

18:16.440 --> 18:17.240
Grandfather.

18:20.620 --> 18:22.410
Grandfather, are you okay?

18:26.200 --> 18:28.070
I just dreamed about

18:28.070 --> 18:30.070
a lot of people who have passed away.

18:31.960 --> 18:33.550
Come on, sit.

18:44.530 --> 18:45.660
Here, Grandfather.

18:50.130 --> 18:51.130
Shi,

18:51.690 --> 18:53.140
tell me,

18:53.650 --> 18:54.940
do you think I

18:55.630 --> 18:57.350
am a good official?

19:00.840 --> 19:01.700
Good official?

19:04.590 --> 19:05.310
You've

19:05.330 --> 19:07.320
simply been worrying too much lately.

19:07.320 --> 19:09.720
It's time you put down
some of your burdens.

19:14.960 --> 19:16.420
Others may not understand

19:16.440 --> 19:18.100
and think you just love power,

19:18.590 --> 19:19.960
but ever since I was little,

19:19.960 --> 19:21.800
I've watched you lie awake
at night worrying about

19:21.800 --> 19:23.150
the prosperity of the Nine Cities.

19:23.150 --> 19:24.730
If you don't qualify as a good official,

19:24.730 --> 19:25.930
then who does?

19:27.360 --> 19:28.390
Shi,

19:30.020 --> 19:32.590
I'm so glad to have you by my side.

19:37.850 --> 19:38.500
Brush and ink.

19:38.500 --> 19:39.470
Bring me the brush and ink.

19:39.470 --> 19:40.130
Right away.

19:49.190 --> 19:51.520
Elder Zheng has been
on leave for days now.

19:51.650 --> 19:53.780
Has his condition still not improved?

19:58.880 --> 19:59.920
Your Excellency,

20:00.320 --> 20:02.880
Lord Zheng's illness
has been quite severe.

20:02.900 --> 20:05.700
He may need to remain bedridden
for a few more days.

20:14.110 --> 20:15.270
Your Excellency,

20:15.960 --> 20:17.290
Lord Zheng is absent.

20:17.810 --> 20:20.740
It's been scorching hot
for days since summer began,

20:21.000 --> 20:24.340
and the transit permits for shipping ice
from Jing City to Ling'an,

20:24.340 --> 20:25.510
as well as

20:26.300 --> 20:28.610
the repair work on
West Bridge outside Ling'an,

20:28.610 --> 20:30.410
have both been delayed for days.

20:30.900 --> 20:31.760
Your Excellency...

20:31.760 --> 20:32.580
Got it!

20:34.110 --> 20:34.870
Next.

20:47.610 --> 20:48.680
Lyu,

20:49.770 --> 20:51.160
Zheng

20:51.940 --> 20:52.900
has fallen ill.

20:52.920 --> 20:55.130
Shouldn't we pay him a visit?

20:55.240 --> 20:55.880
We should.

20:55.880 --> 20:57.140
We definitely should.

20:57.440 --> 20:58.510
I'd like to see for myself

20:58.510 --> 21:00.080
what kind of illness he has

21:00.670 --> 21:02.590
that could make him
set aside the government affairs

21:02.590 --> 21:03.910
he cares so much about.

21:04.460 --> 21:05.220
Right.

21:06.570 --> 21:08.010
At his age,

21:08.640 --> 21:10.300
he just lounges around all day

21:10.350 --> 21:11.350
doing nothing?

21:12.500 --> 21:13.170
He should...

21:13.170 --> 21:14.770
He should get some exercise,

21:14.920 --> 21:15.590
right?

21:16.790 --> 21:17.550
Lyu,

21:18.040 --> 21:19.130
I have to say,

21:19.680 --> 21:20.750
you should

21:20.750 --> 21:22.150
exercise more often too.

21:22.310 --> 21:24.170
You can't spend all day cooped up

21:24.330 --> 21:25.530
in your room reading,

21:25.530 --> 21:26.250
right?

21:26.610 --> 21:27.470
How about this?

21:28.230 --> 21:30.150
When Zheng gets better,

21:30.270 --> 21:32.400
I'll train both of you together.

21:33.160 --> 21:34.310
Look at me now,

21:34.640 --> 21:36.170
strong and healthy as ever!

21:36.600 --> 21:37.860
I eat well, sleep well!

21:39.640 --> 21:40.270
Look.

21:41.570 --> 21:43.400
Let me teach you a couple of moves now.

21:43.400 --> 21:44.160
Look.

21:46.310 --> 21:46.920
Come on.

21:47.440 --> 21:48.030
Come on.

21:51.920 --> 21:53.270
Don't move. Don't move.

21:53.310 --> 21:54.110
What's wrong?

21:54.230 --> 21:54.890
Don't move.

21:55.740 --> 21:57.340
-What's wrong?
-Don't move.

21:57.560 --> 21:59.290
What do you think you're doing?

21:59.630 --> 22:00.960
You have a white beard.

22:02.060 --> 22:03.630
How old are you?

22:03.650 --> 22:05.780
How can you still be so simple-minded?

22:14.180 --> 22:15.990
Well, well, Lyu,

22:16.010 --> 22:17.470
you are insulting me, huh?

22:18.270 --> 22:21.640
Calling me all brawn and no brains?

22:25.480 --> 22:26.930
I'm healthy.

22:26.960 --> 22:28.270
I'm happy.

22:29.960 --> 22:30.590
One,

22:31.110 --> 22:31.720
two,

22:32.150 --> 22:32.750
three!

22:32.780 --> 22:34.020
Look!

22:35.430 --> 22:36.390
See?

22:40.600 --> 22:42.990
What's wrong with being healthy?

22:46.070 --> 22:47.310
Morning, Miss Wei.

22:47.310 --> 22:48.030
Morning.

22:49.880 --> 22:50.590
Miss Wei,

22:50.590 --> 22:51.120
morning.

22:52.310 --> 22:52.960
Morning, Miss Wei.

22:52.640 --> 23:01.500
[Training Grounds]

22:54.100 --> 22:54.750
Miss Wei.

22:55.270 --> 22:56.000
Miss Wei.

22:56.000 --> 22:56.550
Morning.

22:58.000 --> 22:58.590
Morning, Miss Wei.

22:58.590 --> 22:59.960
Morning, Miss Wei.

22:59.960 --> 23:00.510
Miss Wei,

23:00.510 --> 23:01.440
you're here so early.

23:01.440 --> 23:02.440
That couldn't have been easy.

23:02.440 --> 23:04.770
You should hurry along too. Don't be late.

23:15.290 --> 23:16.330
Miss Wei,

23:16.350 --> 23:17.830
you should head back.

23:17.860 --> 23:19.140
As I told you earlier,

23:19.160 --> 23:20.690
we have extra drills today.

23:20.770 --> 23:22.180
Even if you wait here until nightfall,

23:22.180 --> 23:23.980
Lord Gao Ran won't be coming out.

23:24.680 --> 23:25.480
Extra drills?

23:27.110 --> 23:28.110
Why extra drills?

23:28.640 --> 23:30.750
The weather's getting hotter by the day.

23:30.750 --> 23:32.850
The Guardian Corps
have been getting sluggish.

23:32.850 --> 23:35.250
And with Lord Zheng ill
these past few days,

23:35.400 --> 23:37.960
personnel assignments throughout the city
have run into problems.

23:37.960 --> 23:39.290
So at a time like this,

23:39.310 --> 23:41.310
we can't afford to let our guard down.

23:41.310 --> 23:42.200
We need even more training.

23:42.200 --> 23:42.720
Yes.

23:47.480 --> 23:48.880
Does he have heatstroke?

23:49.270 --> 23:50.730
But it's not even that hot.

23:58.680 --> 23:59.610
What's going on?

23:59.790 --> 24:01.120
Are you feeling unwell?

24:01.430 --> 24:02.670
My head is spinning.

24:03.820 --> 24:05.450
I'm seeing stars.

24:05.590 --> 24:06.550
Seeing stars?

24:06.880 --> 24:08.200
Did you skip breakfast today

24:08.200 --> 24:09.200
to rush here?

24:09.830 --> 24:10.720
No.

24:11.420 --> 24:12.480
Before coming in,

24:12.480 --> 24:15.010
I even had a bowl of sour plum drink
at the gate.

24:16.070 --> 24:17.510
Sour plum drink at the gate?

24:17.510 --> 24:18.460
Who made it?

24:25.750 --> 24:26.550
Here you go.

24:26.550 --> 24:27.760
There's enough for everyone!

24:27.760 --> 24:28.860
How is it? Good, right?

24:28.860 --> 24:29.680
I really

24:29.680 --> 24:30.830
went all out with the ingredients.

24:30.830 --> 24:32.150
Thank you, Miss Wei.

24:32.150 --> 24:33.510
You're so considerate of us.

24:33.510 --> 24:35.190
Have another bowl if you like it.

24:35.190 --> 24:35.990
Put that down!

24:51.430 --> 24:52.540
Lord Gao Ran.

24:52.670 --> 24:53.320
Gao Ran,

24:53.350 --> 24:54.740
I knew you'd come out.

24:58.400 --> 24:59.290
My dear sister,

24:59.310 --> 25:01.050
what heavy-duty stuff
did you put in this?

25:01.050 --> 25:01.850
Ginseng

25:01.870 --> 25:02.800
and astragalus.

25:03.670 --> 25:04.840
Such a daring dose.

25:06.000 --> 25:08.080
Putting ginseng and astragalus
into sour plum drink?

25:08.080 --> 25:10.100
No wonder they're all seeing stars.

25:10.230 --> 25:11.290
Is this a gesture of care

25:11.290 --> 25:12.170
or an act of poisoning?

25:12.170 --> 25:12.600
I...

25:13.110 --> 25:14.070
I really didn't know.

25:14.070 --> 25:15.100
I didn't mean to.

25:15.180 --> 25:16.270
Miss Wei,

25:17.010 --> 25:18.070
why did you do this?

25:20.720 --> 25:21.780
I wanted to see you.

25:21.850 --> 25:23.120
You're unbelievable.

25:23.430 --> 25:25.030
This is a military compound.

25:25.400 --> 25:27.790
The soldiers here are carrying out orders.

25:27.790 --> 25:29.070
By law, what you've done

25:29.070 --> 25:30.180
constitutes interference
with military affairs.

25:30.180 --> 25:31.700
You could be punished for it.

25:31.700 --> 25:33.170
I know you care about your soldiers.

25:33.170 --> 25:34.970
But I also want to care about you.

25:40.550 --> 25:42.110
If this is how you express

25:42.110 --> 25:43.410
your care, Miss Wei,

25:43.440 --> 25:45.100
then I'd rather do without it.

25:45.770 --> 25:47.630
Don't show yourself in front of me again.

25:47.630 --> 25:48.420
Gao Ran,

25:49.030 --> 25:50.510
I know you're mad right now.

25:50.510 --> 25:51.110
So whatever you say,

25:51.110 --> 25:52.640
I won't take it to heart.

25:54.510 --> 25:55.370
You, honestly.

25:55.650 --> 25:58.110
You're the daughter
of our noble Wei family.

25:58.240 --> 26:01.200
Why keep throwing yourself at him
when he's clearly not interested?

26:01.200 --> 26:01.920
How do you know

26:01.920 --> 26:04.050
I won't be the one he marries in the end?

26:04.830 --> 26:05.890
Fine, fine.

26:06.210 --> 26:07.280
Keep chasing your romance.

26:07.280 --> 26:08.950
I have more important matters
to attend to.

26:08.950 --> 26:09.700
Handle this stuff

26:09.700 --> 26:10.490
yourself.

26:19.470 --> 26:20.190
Wei Qiao,

26:20.210 --> 26:21.340
take them back.

26:36.920 --> 26:37.980
Help him up quickly.

26:37.980 --> 26:38.940
What's wrong?

26:40.120 --> 26:41.800
Did he get heatstroke?

26:49.680 --> 26:50.740
You're here early.

26:51.350 --> 26:52.180
Alright,

26:52.200 --> 26:53.280
everyone is here.

26:53.670 --> 26:54.400
General Wei,

26:54.850 --> 26:57.120
is there something urgent
you need to discuss with us?

26:57.120 --> 26:58.120
Your Excellency,

26:58.170 --> 26:59.760
due to the extreme heat,
the Guardian Corps

26:59.760 --> 27:01.590
are either falling ill
or neglecting their duties.

27:01.590 --> 27:02.920
As for the policies
meant to address the heatwave,

27:02.920 --> 27:04.800
they're all stalled with Lord Zheng.

27:04.800 --> 27:06.130
It's not just the Guardian Corps.

27:06.130 --> 27:07.000
Lord Zheng

27:07.020 --> 27:08.000
neither attends the morning audience

27:08.000 --> 27:09.510
nor says when he'll return to his post.

27:09.510 --> 27:10.240
There are at least

27:10.240 --> 27:12.790
a dozen vacant positions
waiting to be filled across the city.

27:12.790 --> 27:13.510
Without official orders,

27:13.510 --> 27:15.040
no one can mobilize anyone.

27:16.140 --> 27:17.070
As a result,

27:17.090 --> 27:19.070
officials across every department
are overworked

27:19.070 --> 27:20.000
and collapsing from exhaustion,

27:20.000 --> 27:20.840
which only worsens the situation.

27:20.840 --> 27:22.120
If this continues,

27:22.310 --> 27:23.840
there may soon be no one left
to keep things running.

27:23.840 --> 27:24.510
I think

27:24.910 --> 27:27.260
Lord Zheng's illness is just a pretense.

27:27.350 --> 27:28.680
What he really wants
is to show Your Excellency

27:28.680 --> 27:30.320
and all the officials of the Nine Cities

27:30.320 --> 27:31.500
how dire things become

27:31.500 --> 27:33.110
without him in his post.

27:36.270 --> 27:37.640
The current situation

27:38.550 --> 27:40.920
has made it clear just how much influence
Lord Zheng wields—

27:40.920 --> 27:41.910
without him,

27:42.000 --> 27:43.640
the Nine Cities indeed struggle

27:43.640 --> 27:44.880
to function.

27:46.420 --> 27:47.520
Now it seems

27:47.760 --> 27:49.020
his move

27:49.280 --> 27:50.320
was well played.

27:53.660 --> 27:55.140
Your Excellency has been personally
overseeing governance for quite some time,

27:55.140 --> 27:56.750
yet Lord Zheng still
behaves so arrogantly.

27:56.750 --> 27:59.280
He clearly has no regard for
Your Excellency.

27:59.860 --> 28:00.660
Zheng Yuan

28:00.690 --> 28:03.210
has committed
the crime of insubordination.

28:03.210 --> 28:04.270
Your Excellency was merciful

28:04.270 --> 28:05.400
and spared his life.

28:05.600 --> 28:07.060
Then why not take this opportunity

28:07.060 --> 28:09.070
to strip Zheng Yuan of all his positions?

28:09.070 --> 28:10.070
Without his positions,

28:10.070 --> 28:11.070
he wouldn't be able to play his games.

28:11.070 --> 28:12.270
That would be unwise.

28:13.110 --> 28:14.510
Mr. Zheng has deep roots

28:14.510 --> 28:15.710
among the officials—

28:15.920 --> 28:17.830
a slight move could affect everything.

28:17.830 --> 28:18.720
To solve the problem at its root,

28:18.720 --> 28:20.180
we need careful planning.

28:20.750 --> 28:21.720
But right now,

28:22.000 --> 28:23.600
time is exactly what we lack.

28:28.750 --> 28:29.600
Shi.

28:44.110 --> 28:44.860
Grandfather,

28:44.860 --> 28:45.390
Uncle Yi.

28:46.190 --> 28:47.600
Young Master Shi, you're here.

28:47.600 --> 28:48.490
Let me do it, Uncle Yi.

28:48.490 --> 28:48.880
Okay.

28:52.680 --> 28:53.760
Shi.

28:55.160 --> 28:55.880
Look.

28:55.900 --> 28:57.200
How is

28:57.240 --> 28:58.920
my calligraphy?

28:58.980 --> 29:00.040
I can see your strokes

29:00.040 --> 29:01.300
are vigorous and bold.

29:01.300 --> 29:03.230
So you must be feeling much better.

29:03.790 --> 29:05.550
With you by my side,

29:05.550 --> 29:07.670
of course I recover quickly.

29:07.690 --> 29:08.690
Young Master Shi,

29:09.200 --> 29:10.830
it's the sight of you

29:10.850 --> 29:12.610
that has lifted Master's spirits.

29:12.610 --> 29:13.720
Even this morning,

29:13.750 --> 29:14.820
he was still unsettled by a nightmare.

29:14.820 --> 29:15.890
Nonsense.

29:17.270 --> 29:19.000
And he wouldn't let me tell you.

29:23.140 --> 29:25.470
Are you still dreaming about past events?

29:25.660 --> 29:27.580
When you get old,

29:27.840 --> 29:30.160
the past keeps coming back to mind.

29:32.320 --> 29:33.750
I wonder how things are

29:33.770 --> 29:35.240
at the Qi Residence now.

29:35.260 --> 29:37.100
Lord Lyu and Lord Zhao

29:37.130 --> 29:39.050
are gathering people to
come up with a solution.

29:39.050 --> 29:39.860
I think...

29:40.030 --> 29:42.750
What good solutions can they come up with?

29:42.770 --> 29:44.610
And as for those two...

29:44.640 --> 29:45.900
I still won't see them.

29:53.660 --> 29:57.980
[Void]

30:46.580 --> 30:47.500
Give it to me.

30:56.640 --> 30:58.160
It's getting late.

30:58.850 --> 31:00.650
Why don't you head back and rest?

31:00.890 --> 31:02.400
You don't need to
keep me company all the time.

31:02.400 --> 31:03.550
How could I do that?

31:04.860 --> 31:05.990
I'm not tired at all.

31:07.930 --> 31:09.500
Look at Lord Zheng.

31:10.290 --> 31:11.790
He's been claiming illness

31:11.790 --> 31:13.990
and refusing to hand things over to you.

31:14.710 --> 31:16.910
Now, so many matters have been delayed.

31:21.160 --> 31:22.180
I may not be able

31:23.000 --> 31:24.800
to help you with anything major,

31:25.200 --> 31:26.240
but I can certainly help you

31:26.240 --> 31:28.240
sort through all these documents

31:28.240 --> 31:29.440
and correspondence.

31:29.660 --> 31:31.120
You seem so full of energy.

31:34.810 --> 31:35.960
I mean,

31:35.990 --> 31:37.400
this spirit you have.

31:37.640 --> 31:39.710
Many people, after running into
setback after setback,

31:39.710 --> 31:41.480
eventually become resigned to
their circumstances,

31:41.480 --> 31:43.790
feeling that nothing is worth it anymore.

31:43.790 --> 31:45.120
But you seem different.

31:45.780 --> 31:47.780
No matter what kind of blow you take,

31:48.070 --> 31:50.670
you always pull yourself together
and face it.

31:51.090 --> 31:52.370
Well, we can't just

31:52.390 --> 31:53.420
get all depressed

31:53.450 --> 31:54.610
and blame the heavens

31:54.610 --> 31:56.510
every time things don't go our way, right?

31:56.510 --> 31:57.880
Besides, Lord Wei and Lord Yan

31:57.880 --> 31:59.440
have both picked themselves back up

31:59.440 --> 32:01.970
and are working hard
to resolve things again.

32:02.060 --> 32:03.170
We have to

32:03.200 --> 32:05.330
take things one step at a time, anyway.

32:05.970 --> 32:07.770
We'll deal with whatever comes.

32:12.450 --> 32:13.060
Fan Yun.

32:14.160 --> 32:16.230
Come out of the residence
with me tomorrow, will you?

32:16.230 --> 32:17.690
Come out of the residence?

32:25.920 --> 32:27.230
Governor.

32:27.250 --> 32:28.690
Slow down.

32:32.370 --> 32:33.810
Where exactly are you taking me,

32:33.810 --> 32:35.330
Governor?

32:35.790 --> 32:37.070
We're practically
outside the city already.

32:37.070 --> 32:38.480
We're still not there yet?

32:38.480 --> 32:40.240
I can barely walk anymore.

32:42.400 --> 32:43.240
Did...

32:44.020 --> 32:45.020
you

32:45.040 --> 32:47.040
bring me out here just to relax?

32:47.750 --> 32:49.140
If you want to think of it that way,

32:49.140 --> 32:50.380
that's fine too.

32:54.400 --> 32:55.930
Where exactly are we going?

32:56.590 --> 32:57.270
Governor.

32:57.680 --> 32:58.770
Are you

32:58.790 --> 33:00.480
lost too,

33:00.570 --> 33:01.700
like Lord Yan Jiang?

33:03.900 --> 33:05.300
I'm taking you to a place.

33:05.490 --> 33:06.200
Keep up.

33:06.960 --> 33:08.030
A place?

33:09.440 --> 33:10.700
Governor, wait for me.

33:11.070 --> 33:12.550
I can't walk anymore.

33:15.200 --> 33:16.090
Governor,

33:17.030 --> 33:18.890
when are we going to get there?

33:19.200 --> 33:21.120
I really can't keep going.

33:21.640 --> 33:22.480
I...

33:24.720 --> 33:25.850
Young Master Qiyan?

33:27.690 --> 33:28.270
Why...

33:29.110 --> 33:30.260
Why are you here?

33:30.690 --> 33:31.530
Miss Fan,

33:31.860 --> 33:33.590
could we have a word in private?

33:35.080 --> 33:35.880
In private?

33:35.910 --> 33:37.390
Well, what a small world.

33:38.050 --> 33:39.620
Then let's all talk together.

33:39.620 --> 33:40.260
Yun.

33:40.580 --> 33:41.420
Let's go in.

33:45.180 --> 33:46.350
Why are you here?
